  "id": "guide/i18n-optional-import-global-variants",
  "title": "导入语言环境数据的全局变体",
  "contents": "\n\n\n<div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular-cn/edit/cn/aio/content/guide/i18n-optional-import-global-variants.md?message=docs%3A%20请简述你的修改...\" aria-label=\"提供编辑建议\" title=\"提供编辑建议\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">mode_edit</i></a>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"content\">\n  <h1 id=\"import-global-variants-of-the-locale-data\">Import global variants of the locale data<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/i18n-optional-import-global-variants#import-global-variants-of-the-locale-data\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n<h1 id=\"导入语言环境数据的全局变体\">导入语言环境数据的全局变体<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/i18n-optional-import-global-variants#导入语言环境数据的全局变体\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n<p>The <a href=\"cli\" title=\"CLI Overview and Command Reference | Angular\">Angular CLI</a> automatically includes locale data if you run the <a href=\"cli/build\" title=\"ng build | CLI | Angular\"><code>ng build</code></a> command with the <code>--localize</code> option.</p>\n<p>如果你使用 <code>--localize</code> 选项运行 <a href=\"cli/build\" title=\"ng build | CLI | Angular\"><code>ng build</code></a> 命令，则 <a href=\"cli\" title=\"CLI Overview and Command Reference | Angular\">Angular CLI</a> 会自动包含语言环境数据。</p>\n<!--todo: replace with code-example -->\n<code-example format=\"shell\" language=\"shell\">\n\nng build --localize\n\n</code-example>\n<p>The <code>@angular/common</code> package on npm contains the locale data files.\nGlobal variants of the locale data are available in <a href=\"https://unpkg.com/browse/@angular/common/locales/global\" title=\"@angular/common/locales/global | Unpkg\"><code>@angular/common/locales/global</code></a>.</p>\n<p>npm 上的 <code>@angular/common</code> 包中包含语言环境数据文件。语言环境数据的全局变体来自 <a href=\"https://unpkg.com/browse/@angular/common/locales/global\" title=\"@angular/common/locales/global | Unpkg\"><code>@angular/common/locales/global</code></a>。</p>\n<h2 id=\"import-example-for-french\"><code>import</code> example for French<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/i18n-optional-import-global-variants#import-example-for-french\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n<h2 id=\"法语的-import-示例\">法语的 <code>import</code> 示例<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/i18n-optional-import-global-variants#法语的-import-示例\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n<p>The following example imports the global variants for French (<code>fr</code>).</p>\n<p>以下示例导入了法语 ( <code>fr</code> ) 的全局变体。</p>\n<code-example header=\"src/app/app.module.ts\" path=\"i18n/doc-files/app.module.ts\" region=\"global-locale\">\nimport '@angular/common/locales/<a href=\"api/core/global\" class=\"code-anchor\">global</a>/fr';\n\n</code-example>\n<!-- links -->\n<!-- external links -->\n<!-- end links -->\n\n  <div class=\"reviewed\">最后复查时间： 2/28/2022</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - guide/i18n-optional-overview\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - api/core/global\n - cli\n - cli/build\n - guide/i18n-optional-import-global-variants#import-example-for-french\n - guide/i18n-optional-import-global-variants#import-global-variants-of-the-locale-data\n - guide/i18n-optional-import-global-variants#导入语言环境数据的全局变体\n - guide/i18n-optional-import-global-variants#法语的-import-示例\n - https://github.com/angular/angular-cn/edit/cn/aio/content/guide/i18n-optional-import-global-variants.md?message=docs%3A%20请简述你的修改...\n - https://unpkg.com/browse/@angular/common/locales/global\n-->"
}